"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Is the game really the more realistic the better? Don’t players come to the game just to get pleasure? The reason why people are addicted to games is because they can't get this sense of accomplishment in real life, so developers need to plan and design the gameplay mechanism to make the players indulge, similar to gambling. So is a game world that is infinitely close to the real world really popular?\\n\\n \\n\\nThe early Internet was used by a minority of people , but now everything is connected to the Internet and there is no way to escape the Internet. Will the game be like this in the future? The big game is a decentralized virtual world, but there can also be a layer of games in this game which can be centralized, just like a real-life casino, where players can find pleasure in it.\",\"timestamp\":1641120279,\"title\":\"Capsule（5.5.2021）Game in a Game\"},\"digest\":\"4kGXS_Xpz6K6NqRho4BWTFyMhEDApNN3OlAiPZlG7CM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xE828f8bE1a3CB994133936fB4D9A708a7D192462\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"30oV-kOFSC9lQBdHEarttZfxjliQz8okqoKZUNLBj88\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"oE3PBJa5icihwzV4Vo38ifbPXR099aDCDl_ixLAomho\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"itBRVj1T5fWx_ZNYiowaxda6EHkayYBXzRkD9A2z3wZRuaLaV21UHABBuLJ2RGZeeKuS6hkcb_WiXokaqyBlUg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x31cd513577813d56dac188e35743ecb529db0e03e283593e4cc226acb4e7611a5a06f0e8d95703de997b6dc6c43ffc9841842d11590b5c80d29579b563e532581b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"30oV-kOFSC9lQBdHEarttZfxjliQz8okqoKZUNLBj88\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"oE3PBJa5icihwzV4Vo38ifbPXR099aDCDl_ixLAomho\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"TcbjPW5oMTWcrhzGtf0Qwhj